"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-03-Chinese-swimmer-Yang-Junxuan-back-on-track-before-2024-Summer-Olympics-1uVCBCTUFSo-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Yang Junxuan finishes swimming in the women's 200-meter freestyle final at the 2024 Summer Olympic Trials for Team China in Shenzhen, south China's Guangdong Province, April 21, 2024.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shenzhen\", \"score\": 0.9877896580323133, \"rank\": 0.012360908385928277, \"text\": \"Shenzhen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shenzhen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shenzhen\"}, {\"begin\": 367, \"end\": 372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.743884401858233, \"rank\": 0.34353940566909563, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Guangdong Province\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  Chinese swimmer Yang Junxuan secured her qualification for the upcoming 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris after breaking the women's 100-meter freestyle national record by touching the wall in 52.68 seconds at the country's Olympic Trials in Shenzhen, south China's Guangdong Province, in late April.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 417, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.7658384413370416, \"rank\": 0.3013885216997373, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 433, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Junxuan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yang Junxuan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Junxuan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yang_Junxuan\"}, {\"begin\": 513, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999434012368, \"rank\": 5.6598722707812415e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 655, \"end\": 663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shenzhen\", \"score\": 0.9877896580323133, \"rank\": 0.012360908385928277, \"text\": \"Shenzhen\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shenzhen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shenzhen\"}, {\"begin\": 671, \"end\": 676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.743884401858233, \"rank\": 0.34353940566909563, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Guangdong Province\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guangdong\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yang's performance remains the eighth-best result in the world so far this year.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 795, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"More importantly, it's a good sign that she has bounced back after nearly a year of struggles.\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Yang, she was haunted by central nervous system (CNS) fatigue for months.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 930, \"end\": 958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_nervous_system\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"central nervous system (CNS)\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_nervous_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Central_nervous_system\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a result, she could not move her body freely in the pool and, as a result, could not practice.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In the worst case at that time, after swimming a few hundred meters, I would not be able to lift my arms,\\\" Yang told the China Media Group (CMG).\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1200, \"end\": 1217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I continued, I would need people to rescue me from the pool.\\\"\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What makes CNS fatigue so frustrating was that, unlike normal injuries, it does not have a clear source.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Therefore, Yang, her coach and medical staff did not know where to begin when they tried to fix the problem.\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fortunately for Yang, she managed to recover in the end, and recovered her form before the Olympic Trials.\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1598, \"end\": 1612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"score\": 0.8581582794952675, \"rank\": 0.03896103896103429, \"text\": \"Olympic Trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It made me think a lot about training and competing,\\\" Yang said.\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1680, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I realized that everyone has their own pace.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not need to match others' progress.\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1767, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just need to find my own pace.\\\"\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yang also performed well in the women's 200-meter freestyle event at the Olympic Trials.\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1891, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her time of 1:54.37 is the fourth-best in the world this year.\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1954, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During the pandemic-delayed Tokyo Olympics in 2021, she helped China win gold in the women's 200-meter freestyle relay.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1983, \"end\": 1997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999447482, \"rank\": 5.523909778699115e-11, \"text\": \"Tokyo Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2018, \"end\": 2023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.743884401858233, \"rank\": 0.34353940566909563, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And after three years, she says he has a new understanding of the Games.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can feel that there are more responsibilities and duties on my shoulders,\\\" Yang said.\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's the notion I did not feel before.\\\"\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2542, \"entities\": []}]}"